'''Daystar Craft''' was a manufacturer of [[Airspeeder/Legends|airspeeders]], most notably the [[DC0040 speeder|DC0040]] and [[DC0052 speeder|DC0052]].

==Behind the scenes==
Daystar Craft was introduced by ''[[The Dark Moose]]'' through the ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|''Hyperspace'']].

